% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_loader.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-loader.trx via the tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-loader.trx (Phase 0.6F: scenario loader +
% validate-scenario per GDD section 16), which loads
% examples/bestagon-scenarios/tutorial.bw and asserts:
%
%   1. tutorial.bw loads via `run` without scanner error
%   2. validate-scenario returns 0 errors on canonical tutorial.bw
%   3. Missing required /map-size triggers /missing-key
%   4. Building /pos [200 0] outside 10x10 map triggers /out-of-bounds
%   5. /win-conditions [/not-a-real-name] triggers /unknown-name
%
% Throws on any assertion mismatch.  Runs on default 1 MB VM in < 1 s
% on debug build.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-loader.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
